objectives.description:
To provide comprehensive support to unsupported elders, mentally disabled people and children in one center by addressing their social, economic and psychological problems.

Detailed objectives:
• To provide comprehensive support to unsupported elders over 60 years old in one center continuously;
• To provide comprehensive support to mentally disabled people of all ages in one center and to help them return to productive citizens (to normal) continuously;
• To provide comprehensive support to children under 7 years old and to help them gradually transition to family life when they reach 18 years old;

To continuously work on various fundraising activities to obtain the necessary budget/funds to achieve all these objectives.

